        public EmergencySimulation(double simPeriod,

                           int nbBloodRoom,
                           int nbMRIRoom,
                           int nbRadioRoom)
        EmergencySimulation constructor specifying the simulation time duration and all of the ED's resources
        Parameters:
        simPeriod - the time in which patients can arrive to the ED
        nbPhysicians - number of physicians
        nbNurses - number of nurses
        nbTransporters - number of transporters
        nbBoxRoom - number of box rooms
        nbShockRoom - number of shock rooms
        nbBloodRoom - number of blood rooms
        nbMRIRoom - number of MRI rooms
        nbRadioRoom - number of radio rooms
